# Contact Form API (optional)
# If set, the contact form will POST to this endpoint (Formspree, Netlify Forms, etc.)
# Without it, the form falls back to mailto:contact@slancha.ai
#
# Formspree setup:
#   1. Go to https://formspree.io and create a free account
#   2. Create a new form, get your endpoint URL
#   3. Copy this file to .env and fill in the URL below
#   4. The form will submit JSON and show the success state on 200 OK
#
# VITE_FORM_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID
